## 🏢 Intended Workflow or Task

This prompt is **Step 1** of the planning chain 

- **Trigger:** Script pages 1–18 received from director/production coordinator
- **Actor:** Background art supervisor reviews the extracted location list
- **Timing:** Start of production — before any backgrounds are assigned or built
- **Next step:** P02 (Workload Prioritisation)

```Director sends Tintin script pages 1–18
      ↓
[P01 RUNS — extracts all background locations]
      ↓
Supervisor reviews and approves location list
      ↓
